Interface DtoNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DtoSender
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ClientNode, ServerNode
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface DtoNode
extends DtoSender
    DtoNode is a one-point gateway for incoming and outgoing TransportDto. It extend DtoSender thus sends KeypleDto and contains a DtoHandler for incoming KeypleDto
